headline: Papa John's (PZZA) Surpasses Q4 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Papa John's (PZZA) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 31.25% and 3.46%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
